
Image formats:
 - xpm
 - ico (Windows Icon)
 - (e)ps
 - pcx
 - targa
 - all the others

General:
 - Exif, XMP and ordinary, classic comment support 

Loders:
 - allow for jpeg scaling / orthogonal rotation without recompression

Algorithms:
 - scaling!
 - rotation, descew
 - descreen
 - sharp, unsharp
 - crop
 - all the others

Colorspaces:
 - float, double support
 - CMYK
 - YUV
 - sRGB vs. Adobe RGB
 - ...

Frontends:
 - edentify:
   - more complete
 - edisplay:
   - seperate channels
 - edisplay:
   - channel cycling
   - thumbnailing
   - slideshow

